= Features =
* Generate ctags with F3.
* Add relative numbers in lines with cursor. Change behaviour with F5 key.
* Show netrw menu with Ctr + E. IT is nicely configured to open files in vertical split among others.
* Change between cpp implementation and header files with F4.
* Compile with make using F7.
* Go to definition variable with F12 (use ctags).
* Set kernel coding style stuff when file or dir matches with prefixes "/usr/src" "linux" or "task".

= Install =
* Copy vimrc file in your $HOME/.vimrc
* Copy plugins directory inside a $HOME/.vim directory

